{
  "stem": "14463.4",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He looks at me, who are you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I say, my name is Joseph Weinreich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My God, Father.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who are you with?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where are you from?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, where are you coming from?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, this very minute, we came from Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother and my auntie Mina and the two boys there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He run down like crazy, he took the luggage, put it in his [NON-ENGLISH], you know, down the bottom and he took us upstairs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First we had a shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he gave us something to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we'd all lie down on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Next day, I went with him and you found one room in [INAUDIBLE], somewhere there, you know, we all lived together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I found that place on my trip to Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I found it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we all lived in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Krakow we stayed for nine months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And yeah, the reason why we stayed in Krakow for nine months, because and we were going to go to Israel, to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was no possibility of going to Palestine because you couldn't get any documents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The English didn't allow you to get in, and we were not going to go on a ship, you know, and jump three miles from the shore and swim to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no question about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With two women with three children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, we were going to fix up documents to go to Australia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we immediately wrote to my uncle here, Lester, which was Leisz, actually, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then he guaranteed that he's going to give us work and he's going to look after us when we are in Australia until we, you know, work and whatever.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it took me nine months to get the documentation to go Australia.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
